One architectural refinement

One enhancement I'd make to your overall vision is to make AI an infrastructure capability, not a module. Every service (Loans, Finance, Treasury, HRMS, Risk, GRC) should consume AI through common platform APIs rather than embedding model-specific code. This keeps your business modules independent of specific AI providers and allows you to evolve models over time without rewriting core business logic—a key advantage for a long-lived enterprise platform like ARTH.OS